premise_source_doc_sentence: `` Pilot '' is the first episode of the first season of the American comedy television series The Office , and the show 's first episode overall .
`` Let Me Be Your Star '' is an original song introduced in the first episode of the first season of the musical TV series Smash , entitled Pilot .

In the second season , it was reprised by Karen and several female members of the Bombshell ensemble in the first episode `` On Broadway '' , and by Ivy in the eighth episode `` The Bells and Whistles '' and the eleventh episode `` The Dress Rehearsal '' .
Episode 1  (  The Casual Vacancy  )  ,  (  2015  )  , the first episode of the TV miniseries The Casual Vacancy
The episode was primarily adapted from the first episode of the British series , although it was partially re-scripted in an attempt to `` Americanize '' the new show .
